# Slider Example


```{html}
<div class="slider">
    <div><img src="https://example.com/image1.jpg" alt="Slide 1"></div>
    <div><img src="https://example.com/image2.jpg" alt="Slide 2"></div>
    <!-- Add more slides as needed -->
</div>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        $('.slider').slick({
            slidesToShow: 1,
            slidesToScroll: 1,
            autoplay: true,
            autoplaySpeed: 2000,
            arrows: true,
            dots: true
        });
    });
</script>
```
